User Stories:

As a user, I want to answer questions to learn more about sharks.

As a user, I want to see my score so I can evaluate my shark knowledge.

As a user, I want to see cool sharks while I'm learning to keep me interested.

As a user, I want to know as soon as I answer a question if my answer was correct.

As a user, I want to be able to retake the test if I don't feel my score was high enough.

